      "writtenOn": "2026-02-03T15:58:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There will be different build targets like:\n* high-availability (which will not pack any of these libraries in the plugin jar)\n* high-availability-pubsub-gcp (which will include the GCP client libs)\n* high-availability-pubsub-aws (which will include the AWS SNS+SQS client libs)\n\nIn the end, if *really* needed, we may do a similar thing like you did with the events broker: we may move the core of the high-availability plugin into a module and provide concrete implementations in plugins.",
